source.title: Microsoft Edge upgrades built-in Cloudflare VPN with 5GB of data
source.body: Microsoft's Edge browser has recently enhanced its 'Edge Secure Network' feature, which now offers 5GB of data, significantly increasing from the previously offered 1GB. ...
